title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Junkers JU-52 -  version 1
description:
Today Asobo release the Junkers JU-5 via the marketplace. The place was already announced a while ago and was planned to be available as in parallel with World Update VI but shortly before the release of the world update Asobo announced the plane would be delayed.

But after waiting a little bit longer it is finally here. In this video we will have a quick look at the new plane.

NOTE: we are not going to fly yet but only focus on the exterior and interior in this video.
